      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained by its previous owner. The exterior shows beautifully with a deep shine, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and some light surface scratches near the door handles from normal use. The interior is very clean, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster and all electronics functioning as they should. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a solid service history, making it a dependable choice for its next owner.",
