    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54B32 power plant, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. The high-revving straight-six is mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been proactively addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity under load. The suspension geometry remains true with refreshed bushings, offering the communicative steering and dampened rebound profile essential for spirited driving. While the exterior shows honest signs of road use, the mechanical vitals are robust and the throttle synchronization is sharp, providing a tactile and visceral driving experience for the true purist.",
