      "description": "This meticulously maintained sedan offers a perfect balance of luxury and performance. The exterior features a deep, lustrous finish, though a discerning eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and hood consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery is supple and clean, with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All electronic features, including the dual-zone climate control, heated seats, and the premium navigation system, function flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, backed by a comprehensive service portfolio with all scheduled maintenance performed on time. Recent service includes a full synthetic oil change, a new cabin air filter, and a brake system flush. The tires are matching sets with approximately 70% tread remaining, ensuring a smooth and confident ride. This is a reliable, turn-key vehicle for someone who appreciates documented quality and honest upkeep.",
